      "span_text": "For measuring the average force needed to fracture a leaf at a constant shearing angle of 20° and speed, described and illustrated an apparatus, a calibrated copy of which is available for use at CNRS in Montpellier, France (contact Eric Garnier, email garnier@cefe.cnrs-mop.fr)."
